import { Flex, VStack,  FormControl, Heading,
    Input,
    Stack,
    InputRightElement,
    Button,
    InputGroup,
    FormLabel, } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import {React, useState} from 'react'

const user = {}

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Flex>
        <VStack>
        <FormControl>
            {/* email */}
            <Stack>
                <FormLabel>Email address</FormLabel>
                <Input type='email' />
            </Stack>
            {/* password */}
            <Stack>
                <FormLabel>Email address</FormLabel>
                <Input type='email' />
            </Stack>
        </FormControl>
        </VStack>
    </Flex>
  )
}

export default Login
